{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.1","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:1","prev_osis_id":"Deut.006.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Ordre de d\u00e9truire les Canan\u00e9ens et leurs idoles<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. (Ex 34:11-17. Ps 106:34, etc.) 1 Jn 5:21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019aura fait entrer dans le pays dont tu vas prendre possession, et qu\u2019il chassera devant toi beaucoup de nations, les H\u00e9thiens, les Guirgasiens, les Amor\u00e9ens, les Canan\u00e9ens, les Ph\u00e9r\u00e9ziens, les H\u00e9viens et les J\u00e9busiens, sept nations plus nombreuses et plus puissantes que toi;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.6.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.6.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.2","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:2","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te les aura livr\u00e9es et que tu les auras battues, tu les d\u00e9voueras par interdit, tu ne traiteras point d\u2019alliance avec elles, et tu ne leur feras point gr\u00e2ce.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.3","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:3","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tu ne contracteras point de mariage avec ces peuples, tu ne donneras point tes filles \u00e0 leurs fils, et tu ne prendras point leurs filles pour tes fils;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.4","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:4","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>car ils d\u00e9tourneraient de moi tes fils, qui serviraient d\u2019autres dieux, et la col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019enflammerait contre vous: il te d\u00e9truirait promptement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.5","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:5","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Voici, au contraire, comment vous agirez \u00e0 leur \u00e9gard: vous renverserez leurs autels, vous briserez leurs statues, vous abattrez leurs idoles, et vous br\u00fblerez au feu leurs images taill\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.6","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:6","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-11: cf. (Ex 19:5, 6. 1 Pi 2:9. Tit 2:14.) (De 9:4-6. Jos 23:14-16.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car tu es un peuple saint pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu; l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019a choisi, pour que tu fusses un peuple qui lui appart\u00eent entre tous les peuples qui sont sur la face de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.7","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:7","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ce n\u2019est point parce que vous surpassez en nombre tous les peuples, que l\u2019\u00c9ternel s\u2019est attach\u00e9 \u00e0 vous et qu\u2019il vous a choisis, car vous \u00eates le moindre de tous les peuples.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.8","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:8","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Mais, parce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous aime, parce qu\u2019il a voulu tenir le serment qu\u2019il avait fait \u00e0 vos p\u00e8res, l\u2019\u00c9ternel vous a fait sortir par sa main puissante, vous a d\u00e9livr\u00e9s de la maison de servitude, de la main de Pharaon, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.9","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:9","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Sache donc que c\u2019est l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, qui est Dieu. Ce Dieu fid\u00e8le garde son alliance et sa mis\u00e9ricorde jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la milli\u00e8me g\u00e9n\u00e9ration envers ceux qui l\u2019aiment et qui observent ses commandements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.10","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:10","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mais il use directement de repr\u00e9sailles envers ceux qui le ha\u00efssent, et il les fait p\u00e9rir; il ne diff\u00e8re point envers celui qui le hait, il use directement de repr\u00e9sailles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.11","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:11","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ainsi, observe les commandements, les lois et les ordonnances que je te prescris aujourd\u2019hui, et mets-les en pratique.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.12","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:12","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-26: cf. (De 28:1-14. Ex 23:22-33.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Si vous \u00e9coutez ces ordonnances, si vous les observez et les mettez en pratique, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, gardera envers toi l\u2019alliance et la mis\u00e9ricorde qu\u2019il a jur\u00e9es \u00e0 tes p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.13","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:13","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il t\u2019aimera, il te b\u00e9nira et te multipliera; il b\u00e9nira le fruit de tes entrailles et le fruit de ton sol, ton bl\u00e9, ton mo\u00fbt et ton huile, les port\u00e9es de ton gros et de ton menu b\u00e9tail, dans le pays qu\u2019il a jur\u00e9 \u00e0 tes p\u00e8res de te donner.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.14","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:14","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Tu seras b\u00e9ni plus que tous les peuples; il n\u2019y aura chez toi ni homme ni femme st\u00e9rile, ni b\u00eate st\u00e9rile parmi tes troupeaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.15","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:15","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9loignera de toi toute maladie; il ne t\u2019enverra aucune de ces mauvaises maladies d\u2019\u00c9gypte qui te sont connues, mais il en frappera tous ceux qui te ha\u00efssent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.16","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:16","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Tu d\u00e9voreras tous les peuples que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, va te livrer, tu ne jetteras pas sur eux un regard de piti\u00e9, et tu ne serviras point leurs dieux, car ce serait un pi\u00e8ge pour toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.17","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:17","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Peut-\u00eatre diras-tu dans ton c\u0153ur: Ces nations sont plus nombreuses que moi; comment pourrai-je les chasser?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.18","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:18","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Ne les crains point. Rappelle \u00e0 ton souvenir ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, a fait \u00e0 Pharaon et \u00e0 toute l\u2019\u00c9gypte,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.19","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:19","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>les grandes \u00e9preuves que tes yeux ont vues, les miracles et les prodiges, la main forte et le bras \u00e9tendu, quand l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019a fait sortir: ainsi fera l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, \u00e0 tous les peuples que tu redoutes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.20","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:20","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, enverra m\u00eame les frelons contre eux, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la destruction de ceux qui \u00e9chapperont et qui se cacheront devant toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.19","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.21","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:21","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ne sois point effray\u00e9 \u00e0 cause d\u2019eux; car l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, est au milieu de toi, le Dieu grand et terrible.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.20","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.22","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:22","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, chassera peu \u00e0 peu ces nations loin de ta face; tu ne pourras pas les exterminer promptement, de peur que les b\u00eates des champs ne se multiplient contre toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.21","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.23","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:23","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, te les livrera; et il les mettra compl\u00e8tement en d\u00e9route, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019elles soient d\u00e9truites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.22","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.24","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:24","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il livrera leurs rois entre tes mains, et tu feras dispara\u00eetre leurs noms de dessous les cieux; aucun ne tiendra contre toi, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que tu les aies d\u00e9truits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.23","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.25","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:25","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.007.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Vous br\u00fblerez au feu les images taill\u00e9es de leurs dieux. Tu ne convoiteras point et tu ne prendras point pour toi l\u2019argent et l\u2019or qui sont sur elles, de peur que ces choses ne te deviennent un pi\u00e8ge; car elles sont en abomination \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.26","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.24","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.26","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:26","prev_osis_id":"Deut.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.008.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.7.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Tu n\u2019introduiras point une chose abominable dans ta maison, afin que tu ne sois pas, comme cette chose, d\u00e9vou\u00e9 par interdit; tu l\u2019auras en horreur, tu l\u2019auras en abomination, car c\u2019est une chose d\u00e9vou\u00e9e par interdit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.8.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.8.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.7.25","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb2bb45f9.26347454');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2bb45f9.26347454\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb2bb45f9.26347454","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb2bb45f9.26347454'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2bb45f9.26347454\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}